section.div: Favorites genres: Action, Fantasy, Adventure, Drama

div.div:
After losing his family and becoming void of emotion but hatred, just wanted to kill the monsters he loathed.
I, Noh Eunha, regressed before my life ended in the deepest part of the Abyss Dungeon that was impossible for mankind to raid.
Since I’ve been reborn as a baby, let’s make this life different.
I will do anything for the sake of my happiness. I’ll kill in order to live, I’ll do my best to survive.
Even if I have to walk a thorny path by myself without anyone acknowledging me.
In this life, I will definitely—
SSS-geup Teukseongeul Badatjiman Jeokdanghi Salgo Sipda

The world now swarms with supernatural beings called Celestials and the Awakened, people with newfound special powers. But none of this means anything to Yoo Sungwon, an ordinary man trying to live an ordinary life. Unfortunately for him, his peaceful days end when he gets a mysterious text and becomes a rare SSS-class knight with perks to die for. In order to avoid getting killed or targeted by those who want his powers for their own, Sungwon has no choice but to get stronger by leveling up.
(Source: Tapas)
